        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter">
                    <ab><title>Exodus 30</title>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="7" />
                        <l xml:id="Ex-030-x001"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;"
                                >ל </foreign>
                        </l><l n="1" xml:id="Ex-030-001"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ועשית</foreign>
                            <milestone unit="line" n="8" />
                            Da qylɣyn mizbeaḥ titetme titsi šitim aɣaclaryndan qylɣyn any.</l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="9" />
                        <l n="2" xml:id="Ex-030-002"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">אמה </foreign>
                            Lokot uzunluɣu da lokot könligi anyn dert tirli bolsun
                            <milestone unit="line" n="10" />
                            da eki lokotler turusu anyn andan bolsunlar mivizleri anyn.</l><l n="3"
                            xml:id="Ex-030-003"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;"
                                >וצפית</foreign>
                            <milestone unit="line" n="11" />
                            Da qaplaɣyn any aruv altyn byla osol cardaɣyn anyn da osol farst-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="12" />
                            lary anyn civre da osol mivizlerin anyn da qylɣyn anar altyn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="13" />
                            qursov civre.</l><l n="4" xml:id="Ex-030-004"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ושתי </foreign>
                            Da eki izikler altyn qylɣyn anar asaɣar-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="14" />
                            tyn qursovuna anyn eki janlary istine anyn qylɣyn eki mivis-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="15" />
                            leri istine anyn da bolsun orunlar tutquclarɣa eltme any
                            <milestone unit="line" n="16" />
                            alar byla.</l><l n="5" xml:id="Ex-030-005"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ועשית </foreign>
                            Da qylɣyn osol ol tutquclarny šitim
                            <milestone unit="line" n="17" />
                            aɣaclaryndan da qapaɣyn alarny altyn byla.</l><l n="6"
                            xml:id="Ex-030-006"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;"
                                >ונתת </foreign>
                            Da bergin
                            <milestone unit="line" n="18" />
                            any alnynda ol paroḫetnin ki aronu istine ol sarajatnyn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="19" />
                            alnynda ol kaporetnin ki ol sarajat istine ki jomulurmen sana ary.</l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="20" />
                        <l n="7" xml:id="Ex-030-007"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">והקטיר </foreign>
                            Da titetsin anyn istine Aharon titsisin otjamlar-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="21" />
                            nyn har erten bylada tizetkeninde osol ol cyraqlarny tit-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="22" />
                            etsin an.</l><l n="8" xml:id="Ex-030-008"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ובהעלות </foreign>
                            Da jandyrɣanda Aharon osol ol cyraq-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="23" />
                            larny ol eki ingirler arasyna titetsin any hammešelik titsi
                            <milestone unit="line" n="24" />
                            alnynda H-nyn dorlarynyz sajyn.</l><l n="9" xml:id="Ex-030-009"><foreign
                                xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">לא </foreign>
                            Mindirmeniz anyn istine
                            <milestone unit="line" n="25" />
                            jat titsi da ʿola da tirki da neseḫ qojmanyz anyn istine.</l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="26" />
                        <l n="10" xml:id="Ex-030-010"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">וכפר </foreign>
                            Da bosatlyq qolsun Aharon mivizleri ücün anyn bir
                            <milestone unit="line" n="27" />
                            keret jylda qanyndan ol bosatlyqlarnyn bir keret jylda
                            <milestone unit="page" n="92v" />
                            <milestone unit="line" n="1" />
                            bosatlyq qolsun anyn ücün dorlarynyz sajyn qodeš qadašim ol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="2" />
                            Adonajɣa.
                            <milestone unit="line" n="3" />
                            פפפ
                            <milestone unit="line" n="4" />
                            <foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">פרשת כי
                                תשא</foreign>
                        </l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="5" />
                        <l n="11" xml:id="Ex-030-011"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">וידבר ה֘ אל משה לאמר</foreign>
                            <milestone unit="line" n="6" />
                            Da sözledi H Mošege ajtadoɣac.</l><l n="12" xml:id="Ex-030-012"><foreign
                                xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">כי </foreign>
                            Ki sanyn alsan osol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="7" />
                            sanyn basynyn uvullarynyn Jisraʾelnin sanalɣanlary sajyn da
                            <milestone unit="line" n="8" />
                            bersinler kisi juluvuun ʒanynyn H-ɣa sanaɣanda alarny da bolma-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="9" />
                            syn alarda qyranc sanaɣanda alarny.</l><l n="13" xml:id="Ex-030-013"
                                ><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">זה </foreign>
                            Bunu bersinler bar
                            <milestone unit="line" n="10" />
                            ol asuvcu ol sanalɣanlar asyra jarymyn ol mitqalnyn ol aziz
                            <milestone unit="line" n="11" />
                            mitqal byla egirmi gegdi ol mitqal jarymyn ol mitqalnyn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="12" />
                            teruma H-ɣa.</l><l n="14" xml:id="Ex-030-014"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">כל </foreign>
                            Bar ol asuvcu ol sanalɣan qatyna
                            <milestone unit="line" n="13" />
                            egirmi jastan da joɣarraq bersin terumasyn H-nyn.</l><l n="15"
                            xml:id="Ex-030-015"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;"
                                >העשיר </foreign>
                            Ol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="14" />
                            arttyrmasyn da ol jarly az etmesin jarymyndan ol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="15" />
                            mitqalnyn berme osol terumasyn H-nyn bosatlyq qolma ʒanlary-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="16" />
                            nyz ücün.</l><l n="16" xml:id="Ex-030-016"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ולקחת </foreign>
                            Da alɣyn osol kimisin ol bosatlyqlarnyn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="17" />
                            osol uvullaryndan Jisraʾelnin da bergin any qulluɣuna ohel moʿed-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="18" />
                            nin da bolsun uvullarnuna Jisraʾelnin saɣynclyqqa alnynda H-nyn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="19" />
                            bosatlyq qolma ʒanlarynyz ücün siznin.</l><l n="17" xml:id="Ex-030-017"
                                ><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">וידבר </foreign>
                            Da sözledi
                            <milestone unit="line" n="20" />
                            H Mošege ajtadoɣac.</l><l n="18" xml:id="Ex-030-018"><foreign
                                xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ועשית </foreign>
                            Da qylɣyn qumɣan tuʒlu da ornun
                            <milestone unit="line" n="21" />
                            anyn tyʒlu juvunmaqqa da bergin anyn arasyna ohel moʿednin da
                            <milestone unit="line" n="22" />
                            arasyna ol mizbeaḥnyn da bergin ary suvlar.</l><l n="19"
                            xml:id="Ex-030-019"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;"
                                >ורחצו </foreign>
                            Da juvsunlar
                            <milestone unit="line" n="23" />
                            Aharon da uvullary anyn andan osol qollaryn da osol ajaqlaryn.</l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="24" />
                        <l n="20" xml:id="Ex-030-020"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">בבואם </foreign>
                            Kelgenlerinde ohel moʿedge juvsunlar guflaryn suvlar-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="25" />
                            byla da elmesinler jemese juvuɣanlarynda ol mizbeaḥqa jumus-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="26" />
                            etme titetme otlu qarban H-ɣa.</l><l n="21" xml:id="Ex-030-021"><foreign
                                xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ורחצו </foreign>
                            Da juvsunlar
                            <milestone unit="line" n="27" />
                            qollaryn
                            <milestone unit="page" n="93r" />
                            <milestone unit="line" n="1" />
                            qollaryn da ajaqlaryn da elmesinler da bolsun alarɣa emir-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="2" />
                            lik resim anar da urluɣuna anyn dorlary sajyn.</l><l n="22"
                            xml:id="Ex-030-022"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;"
                                >וידבר </foreign>
                            Da
                            <milestone unit="line" n="3" />
                            sözledi H Mošege ajtadoɣac.</l><l n="23" xml:id="Ex-030-023"><foreign
                                xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ואתה </foreign>
                            Da sen alɣyn jüzüne ilk
                            <milestone unit="line" n="4" />
                            otjamlar musq ijisli bes iz mitqal da cynamon ijisli jarymyn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="5" />
                            anyn eki iz enli mitqal da qorqa ijisli eki iz enli mitkqal.</l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="6" />
                        <l n="24" xml:id="Ex-030-024"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">וקדה </foreign>
                            Da qasja (<ref target="#fn1" type="noteAnchor" /><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">או פ֮א </foreign>
                            hvozdik) bes iz ol aziz mitqal
                            <milestone unit="line" n="7" />
                            byla da zejtun hin.</l><l n="25" xml:id="Ex-030-025"><foreign
                                xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ועשית </foreign>
                            Da qylɣyn andan sirtilmis
                            <milestone unit="line" n="8" />
                            jav aziz maʒun maʒunlanɣan isin maʒunlavcunun sirtilmis jav
                            <milestone unit="line" n="9" />
                            aziz bolsun.</l><l n="26" xml:id="Ex-030-026"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ומשחת </foreign>
                            Da jaqqyn anyn byla osol ol moʿedni
                            <milestone unit="line" n="10" />
                            da osol aronun ol sarajatnyn.</l><l n="27" xml:id="Ex-030-027"><foreign
                                xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ואת </foreign>
                            Da osol ol stolnu
                            <milestone unit="line" n="11" />
                            da osol bar savutlaryn anyn da osol ol cyraqbany da osol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="12" />
                            savutlaryn anyn da osol mizbeaḥyn ol titsinin.</l><l n="28"
                            xml:id="Ex-030-028"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;"
                                >ואת </foreign>
                            Da osol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="13" />
                            mizbeaḥyn ol ʿolanyn da osol bar savutlaryn anyn da osol ol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="14" />
                            qumɣanny da osol orunun anyn.</l><l n="29" xml:id="Ex-030-029"><foreign
                                xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">וקדשת </foreign>
                            Da aziz etkin alarny
                            <milestone unit="line" n="15" />
                            da bolsunlar qodeš qadašim bar ol tijivcü alarɣa kereklidi ki aziz-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="16" />
                            lengej.</l><l n="30" xml:id="Ex-030-030"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ואת </foreign>
                            Da osol Aharonnu da osol uvullaryn anyn jaqqyn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="17" />
                            da aziz etkin alarny kohenlik etme mana.</l><l n="31"
                            xml:id="Ex-030-031"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;"
                                >ואל </foreign>
                            Da uvullaryn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="18" />
                            Jisraʾelnin sözlegin ajtadoɣac sirtilmis jav aziz bolsun bu mana
                            <milestone unit="line" n="19" />
                            dorlarynyz sajyn.</l><l n="32" xml:id="Ex-030-032"><foreign
                                xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">על </foreign>
                            Gufu istine adamyn jaɣylmasyn da qyjasy
                            <milestone unit="line" n="20" />
                            byla anyn qylmanyz anyn kibik azizdi ol aziz bolsun sizge.</l><l n="33"
                            xml:id="Ex-030-033"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;"
                                >איש</foreign>
                            <milestone unit="line" n="21" />
                            Kisi ki maʒunlasa anyn kibikni qylma da ki berse andan jat
                            <milestone unit="line" n="22" />
                            istine da eksilsin uluslaryndan.</l><l n="34" xml:id="Ex-030-034"
                                ><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויאמר </foreign>
                            Da ajtty
                            <milestone unit="line" n="23" />
                            H Mošege alɣyn ezine otjamlar musq da revend da galban
                            <milestone unit="line" n="24" />
                            otjamlar da aruv levona teppeten bolsun <foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">פשט אחר על מלת ב֒ד בב֒ד </foreign>
                            <milestone unit="line" n="25" />
                            <foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">מפשט הר֘ר שמחה בכמ
                                חננאל זצו֘קל</foreign>
                            <ref target="#fn2" type="noteAnchor" /> basqa basqa bolsun.</l><l n="35"
                            xml:id="Ex-030-035"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;"
                                >ועשית </foreign>
                            Da qylɣyn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="26" />
                            any titsi maʒun isin maʒunlavcunun qosulɣan aruv aziz.</l><l n="36"
                            xml:id="Ex-030-036"><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;"
                                >ושחקת</foreign>
                            <milestone unit="line" n="27" />
                            Da jancqyn andan uvaq da bergin andan alnynda ol sarajatnyn
                            <milestone unit="page" n="93v" />
                            <milestone unit="line" n="1" />
                            ohel moʿedde ki jumulumen sana ary qodeš qadašim bolsun sizge.</l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="2" />
                        <l n="37" xml:id="Ex-030-037"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">והקטרת </foreign>
                            Da ol titsi ki qylsan qyjasy byla anyn qylmanyz
                            <milestone unit="line" n="3" />
                            ezinizge aziz bolsun sana H-ɣa.</l><l n="38" xml:id="Ex-030-038"
                                ><foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">איש </foreign>
                            Kisi ki qylsa anyn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="4" />
                            kibik ijiskeme anyn byla da eksilsin uluslaryndan.</l></ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="apparatus">
                <listApp>
                    <app>
                        <note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote">Heb. abbreviation of <foreign
                                xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">או </foreign>
                            פּ<foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ֵיר</foreign>
                            וּשׁ <foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">אַחֵר </foreign>
                            ‘or another explanation [interpretation]’. Here perhaps as <foreign
                                xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">או </foreign>
                            פּ<foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ְשָט אַחֵר </foreign>
                            ‘or another translation’.</note>
                        <note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote">Heb. ‘Another translation of the words
                                <emph>baḏ bəḇaḏ</emph> ‘equal amounts of each’ from a translation of
                            our master and rabbi Simḥa the son of the honourable sir Ḥananʾel may
                            the memory of the righteous and saint be blessed’.</note>
                    </app>
                </listApp>
            </div>
